description: Try our easy to follow Dukkah recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Dukkah Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400g Woolworths stone baked Turkish pide loaf, toasted (to serve)

recipeInstructions.text: Fry 2 tbs sesame seeds, 1 tbs coriander seeds, 1 tbs cumin seeds, 2 tsp black peppercorns and 1 tsp fennel seeds in a dry frying pan until fragrant.
Place mixture into a food processor with 50g roasted hazelnuts and 1 tsp dried mint. Process coarsely.
Transfer to a serving bowl. Serve with a small bowl of olive oil and pieces of toasted turkish bread.
